<h3>7.1 Cancellation</h3>
<p>
  You may cancel recurring donations at any time. Cancellation applies only to future scheduled donations. <strong>Donations that have already been processed are not refundable due to cancellation.</strong>
</p>

<h3>7.2 Methods to Cancel</h3>
<p>You may cancel recurring donations through the following methods:</p>
