<h3>7.3 Processing Time</h3>
<p>
  Cancellation requests require up to <strong>two (2) business days</strong> to process. <strong>If a scheduled donation is processed before your cancellation request is complete, you are responsible for that donation and it will not be refunded.</strong> To ensure a donation is not processed, submit your cancellation request at least <strong>five (5) business days</strong> before the scheduled donation date.
</p>

