</p>
<p>
  <strong>We do not provide tax advice. You are solely responsible for consulting with a qualified tax professional regarding the tax treatment of refunded donations.</strong>
</p>

<h2>9. Non-Refundable Circumstances</h2>
<p><strong>The following circumstances do not qualify for refunds:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Change of mind or donor's remorse</li>
  <li>Dissatisfaction with how funds are used (all general donations support the Organization's overall ministry unless specifically designated)</li>
  <li>Requests submitted after the deadline periods specified in this policy</li>
  <li>Donations made through third-party platforms not operated by the Operator</li>
  <li>Claims of financial hardship arising after the donation was made</li>
  <li>Disputes regarding the tax-deductibility of donations</li>
  <li>Disputes arising from the donor's failure to review transaction details before confirming</li>
</ul>

